#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Standalone ROBIN watermark benchmark (Huang et al. 2024).

Generation-based: watermarked images from SD2.1 + optimized latent patch (opt_wm).
Clean unwatermarked images use the same prompt/latent seed without injection.

Metrics per attack:
  - PSNR, SSIM (watermarked vs watermarked+attacked)
  - AUROC, TPR @ 1% FPR (score = 1 / (1 + FFT patch L1 distance))
  - bit_accuracy: N/A (latent-ring style detector, no bit payload)

Attacks: benchmark_attacks.py (14 WAVES attacks, unchanged).

Example (full pipeline — generate + detect):
  D:\\waves\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe mainbenchmark ^
      --n-images 100 ^
      --output outputs_benchmark

Example (detect only — use pre-generated image folders):
  D:\\waves\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe mainbenchmark ^
      --detect-only ^
      --wm-dir path/to/watermarked ^
      --clean-dir path/to/clean ^
      --output outputs_benchmark_detect

Example (detect only — single folder with wm_image_* + clean_image_*):
  D:\\waves\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe mainbenchmark ^
      --detect-only ^
      --image-dir D:\\waves\\robinresults\\images ^
      --output D:\\waves\\robinresults\\benchmark
"""
